{"tid":2271193,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[燈呀NMSL] 老老實實 侵侵已經輸左 拜登270-268侵侵","createTime":"2020-11-04T12:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T13:06:02.000Z","uid":110109,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8902e40654b5d5cf6c6b9ebf2986451ba0ada37f","tid":2271193,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T12:19:59.000Z","msg":"老老實實 侵侵已經輸左 拜登270-268侵侵<br />\n<br />\n當T侵侵已經已經贏左PA<br />\n<br />\nME同NE既split vote, 比埋侵侵favor, 3-2拜登<br />\n<br />\n而家得返GA, WI, MI呢3個州左右大局<br />\n<br />\nWI已經比拜登反CUP左 - 10票<br />\n<br />\nGA當比TRUMP攞 - 16票<br />\n<br />\n即係254-268<br />\n<br />\nTRUMP唔夠270<br />\n<br />\n要靠MI, <br />\n<br />\nMI而家開左92%票 總票數係4661606 <br />\n<br />\n即係總票數約為5,066,963票<br />\n<br />\n侵侵LEAD緊 102,134票<br />\n<br />\n剩低既8%票= 405357張<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMI最多票未開既係DETROIT既票箱 其次仲有一D細少少既COUNTY<br />\n<br />\nDETROIT總共約有廿萬張票未開<br />\n<br />\nDETROIT已經開左既票入面 拜登:侵侵既比例大約係8:2<br />\n<br />\n即係16萬:4萬 <br />\n<br />\n呢到拜登可以贏翻12張票 已經夠佢同侵侵係MI打和<br />\n<br />\n所以好大機會侵係會輸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4f6e41c8ca5d915ce2a48821210c190b00d896","tid":2271193,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T12:20:14.000Z","msg":"集氣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a61637df11259737e1b52f8d8df604a674b8e9","tid":2271193,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T1